Add feature descriptions to the User Guide This commit adds a comprehensive section to the User Guide that outlines the key features of the Tran$act application. The features are described in detail, providing users with a clear understanding of what the application offers. The added content covers features related to adding transactions, removing transactions, viewing all transactions, editing transactions, restoring deleted transactions, dashboard display, access to financial reports, customizable reports, data security and backup, and the address book. These features are tailored to the needs of accountants and finance professionals in small businesses, offering efficient data entry and financial reporting capabilities.
